title: 820-00165 CPU high temperature.
message: I just changed the thermal folder, now it is not turning on. When I remove the Q8150, it turns on again. It already replaces R8166, R8165, C1950 and U1950, but it's still intermittent.  ALL_SYS 0.012V; PPbus 8.6V; PP3v42 3.42V.

title: 820-00165 CPU high temperature.
message: Leave Q8150 out of board; redundant protection, not really needed.
